{"tid":140983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【田生不作虧心事】黑幫佔田生單位　香檳大廈10劏54房闢黃賭毒場所","createTime":"2017-03-02T14:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T15:05:40.000Z","uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdcb705d98414fa0cd49686c7ee3188ed2c0c681","tid":140983,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/451903/xlarge/9e1384e5d2c8badff6e1125661481049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F451903%2Fxlarge%2F9e1384e5d2c8badff6e1125661481049.jpg&h=d0d8ad36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/75429/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F75429%2F&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=957acb05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/75429/</a><br />\n尖沙嘴香檳大廈以「一樓一鳳」聞名，自2011年起被田生集團（現易名為宏輝集團）大規模收購等候重建，惟有3個黑幫堂口和勝和、14K和新義安肆意攤分肥肉，趁機非法佔領空置單位，經營賣淫場所、毒窟、賭檔和武器庫，嚴重影響區內治安。警方接手追查，今（2日）於香檳大廈進行大規模反罪惡行動，出動反黑組、機動部隊、警犬組、特別職務隊及特遣隊，搗破10個被劏成54個房間的霸佔單位，並拘捕3人，估計已斷絕黑幫每月逾千萬元收入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/451908/xlarge/9decb0cbc0398d906b993f90def9e543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F451908%2Fxlarge%2F9decb0cbc0398d906b993f90def9e543.jpg&h=d0a8fdcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油尖警區助理指揮官（刑事）羅國凱警司表示，尖沙咀金巴利道16號香檳大廈B座自去年起，先後發生多宗包括傷人、爆竊、行劫及刑毀等嚴重罪案，警方經調查後，得悉大廈有達7成業權被收購，惟有關單位一直空置，卻被不同黑幫背景人士趁機非法霸佔至少10個單位，並將單位劏成約54個細房出租，經營賣淫、毒窟、武器庫、賭檔等非法用途。警方粗略估計，黑幫每月單算賣淫已賺逾千萬元收入。<br />\n<br />\n羅指出，油尖警區早前已加大力度派員巡邏，至今午出動警區反黑組、特別職務隊、特遣隊、機動部隊及警犬組人員採取聯合反罪惡行動，突擊搜查至少10個位於2至8樓的被霸佔單位，以涉嫌干犯毒品和被法庭通緝拘捕2名40歲姓鄧和45歲姓黃男子，又以涉嫌違反逗留條件拘捕1名27歲泰籍女子。警方於行動中檢獲一批懷疑毒品、吸食工具、武器、賭博及爆竊工具等，行動至今晚仍在進行。據了解，負責收購上址項目為田生集團有限公司，現已改名為宏輝集團控股有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/451898/xlarge/3c6c9bbdf1a6e332679af9b7ac3b396f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F451898%2Fxlarge%2F3c6c9bbdf1a6e332679af9b7ac3b396f.jpg&h=732a9ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n業主代表黃先生（左）指曾接到很多投訴，指他們持有的單位遭人非法霸佔。（余睿菁攝）<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，香檳大廈於2011年開始被大規模收購，而有關大廈併購一直是田生集團有限公司執行（現改名為宏輝集團控股有限公司），因此坊間一直盛傳恒基有意全面收購香檳大廈，等候重建。大業主代表黃先生及其代表律師陳曼琪表示，去年曾接到很多投訴，指他們持有的單位遭人非法霸佔，並進行違法行為，嚴重影響區內治安，遂今日配合警方行動。查冊顯示，其中一個被「佔領」的單位，由高遠投資有限公司收購, 董事陳佩敏及邵錦熙, 料是田生地產或有關人士。"},{"pid":"5800b39721f92497732866fd1dc66ebdc360728a","tid":140983,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:34:23.000Z","msg":"差佬訓左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ca316746e56575c10e688ba617259464895abe","tid":140983,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差佬訓左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢單野係話俾人知<br />\n有其他老黑霸左田生間屋黎攪黃賭毒<br />\n差佬先至會做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457ac837f595a2aed345b3841a9f1e55cc99f95c","tid":140983,"uid":4112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H46r35O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH46r35O.jpg&h=aa1bce97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e836d7c8f007ec36d526f95b89ad828433d435d","tid":140983,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"不如掃晒香港所有鳳樓呀"},{"pid":"e3faed0b1d8fef43171786bd3b7df055401e4480","tid":140983,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如掃晒香港所有鳳樓呀</blockquote><br />\n唔知會唔會係田生報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915ef8b19ee1e0011871869da6027b1fe24b7b82","tid":140983,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H46r35O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH46r35O.jpg&h=aa1bce97&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f480b69f534bfab05edc8354cfa9128ee9dc8f3c","tid":140983,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"相入面係咪有陳曼琪依條死臭屄？"},{"pid":"408685ee9becdb6657975148a9909134d6f851c8","tid":140983,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相入面係咪有陳曼琪依條死臭屄？</blockquote><br />\n陳曼琪好似係幫恆基做野"},{"pid":"cb56c3bf1e5b0dd45df944e3c4033705c28317c0","tid":140983,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H46r35O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH46r35O.jpg&h=aa1bce97&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636fa4135f4e71468480fdba9bcec9de42ff3b5b","tid":140983,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c88afd657bdff0b932d3dd3ae33fbc108b39d093","tid":140983,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H46r35O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH46r35O.jpg&h=aa1bce97&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑警：阿媽，我得咗啦</blockquote><br />\n猶太人：條女好得噃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}